bullet_point.value: HANDCRAFTED GENUINE LEATHER: The men's wedge sole boots are handcrafted with a premium full-grain oiled leather upper for increased durability, as well as double stitched seams and leather reinforcements that offer style and gives added protection

COMFORTABLE FOOTWEAR: Known to create quality handcrafted footwear that are enjoyable to use and innovative in style, the leather work boots for men are designed with comfort in mind and with all the components you can expect from Twisted X

BREATHABLE AND MOISTURE-WICKING. The wedge work boots are air-mesh lined, allowing air to circulate in and around the shoe while managing moisture; The SD footbed of the lace up boots are also machine washable, looking new every time

DURABILITY AND IMPROVE TRACTION: The composite XD insole provides the wedge sole boots with unrivaled support and stability, while the molded rubber outsole gives it a slip-resistant feature that also provides added durability and improved traction

VERSATILE STYLE: The Twisted X boots offer a fresh take on an iconic style, offering all of today's modern comforts while retaining its timeless appeal; These leather work boots are ready for any occasion, perfectly matching your outfit of the day
